date: Tue Feb 15 2022 01:38:45 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
description: Radio shock jock Kyle Sandilands and fiance Tegan Kynaston are expecting their first child. The couple don't know the sex of the baby, who is due in August, but have already decided on boy and girl names. The 50-year-old KIIS FM presenter made the announcement on his radio show, The Kyle & Jackie O Show.
